hopobject.body: What part of do you come from? betapace medscape This will not sound in the least extreme to anyone who has been afflicted by the condition. At the most banal level, one wonders what one would look like with sleep (younger, surely?), one fantasises that one would eat and drink more wisely sans lag, function better, be less of a bitch. While, at a less banal level, there are moments when sleeplessness feels akin to madness, or mental illness.
